headline: Haemonetics (HAE) Tops Q2 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Haemonetics (HAE) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 2.75% and 0.73%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
